mportant;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-01%2021%3A04%3A515.jpg?Expires=2035199092&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2FAFRsff58A0vMAb%2FJx9hADIy%2BBc%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-01%2021%3A04%3A515.jpg?Expires=2035199092&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2FAFRsff58A0vMAb%2FJx9hADIy%2BBc%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">与会领导为“十佳优秀毕业生”颁发了荣誉证书以及华为平板电脑和笔记本电脑等奖品。先锋软件集团领导、学校领导及校学位评定委员会委员为每一位毕业生拨穗，颁发学位证书，并与他们合影留念，记录下这一人生的重要时刻。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-01%2021%3A08%3A066.jpg?Expires=2035199286&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Bi1mcyvaVuAEmDfth2CShWLWRF8%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-01%2021%3A08%3A066.jpg?Expires=2035199286&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Bi1mcyvaVuAEmDfth2CShWLWRF8%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -w